CB Richard Ellis to Buy Majority of ING Real Estate Units for $940 Million

-- B y   J o A n n e   N o r t o n
-- 
2011-02-15T13:08:21Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-15/cb-richard-ellis-to-buy-majority-of-ing-real-estate-units-for-940-million.html
  CB Richard Ellis Group Inc . said it
agreed to acquire the majority of the real estate investment
management business of Netherlands-based ING Group NV for about
$940 million in cash.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
